  "source": "[\\weak.initial.segment:in{X}:of{a}]\nDefines: S is \\set\nwhen:\n. X is \\set\n. a is \\set\n. a \"in\" X\nexpresses:\n. forAll: x is \\set\n  then:\n  . have:\n    . allOf:\n      . x \"in\" X\n      . x \\:precedes:/ a\n    iff: x \"in\" S\nDocumented:\n. called: \"weak initial segment of $a?$\"\n. written: \"\\overline{s}(a?)\"\n. description: \"The weak initial segment $\\overline{s}(a) = \\{x \\in X \\mid x \\preceq a\\}$ of an element $a$ in a partially ordered set $X$.\"\nId: \"352c164f-8ad4-4747-916a-2938c0888ae5\"",
